  m_text: "King: States if they are next to at least one safe character. Could be
    one ghost and one subject, or two subjects\r\n\nMaid: States a character is a
    ghost. Will always select subjects if lying, or ghosts if telling the truth\r\n\nManservant:
    States a character is a subject. Will always select ghosts if lying, or subjects
    if telling the truth\r\n\nBard: States how far away they are from the closest
    ghost. If lying, states how far away they are from the closest subject \r\n\nExecutioner:
    the second character is a subject if and only if the first is a subject. If lying,
    the second character is a ghost"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 241c6acceca8b844baad6cbcf60cefc7, type: 2}
